    {
      "datasheetId": "000002780",
      "line": 2,
      "button": "•",
      "description": "The Kill Team Sergeant can replace its close combat weapon with one of the following:\n\n• 1 Astartes chainsword\n• 1 power fist\n• 1 power weapon\n• 1 thunder hammer"
    },
    {
      "datasheetId": "000002780",
      "line": 3,
      "button": "•",
      "description": "For every 5 models in this unit, 1 model equipped with a Deathwatch bolt rifle can be equipped with 1 Astartes grenade launcher."
    },
    {
